I asked the group leaders I selected to create good and balanced groups and gave each a chance to make a group one at a time.  I did this to take the job of making groups from myself to those.  The best way I think is to do a /who silver and a /who seekers then have the raid leader, me, make the groups.  Those that show as in Emain are put in groups and it is easy to scroll through the names to do this.  I took a shortcut and did so to make this part go faster, we had already delayed that night and giving people something to do makes it seem to go faster.   No one should have selected all of any type for their group and as they did they erred in selection.<br>
